"EKES"."EINDT" , "EKES"."EBTYP" = 'AB' ) , 'YYYYMMDD' ) , TO_TIMESTAMP ( '13-01-2020' , 'DD-MM-YYYY' ) ) ) >= 0 THEN 'No Goods Receipt and Future Due Date' WHEN ISNULL ( PU_LAST ( "EKPO" , ) = 1 AND ( DATEDIFF ( dd , TO_TIMESTAMP ( PU_LAST ( "EKPO" , "EKES"."EINDT" , "EKES"."EBTYP" = 'AB' ) , 'YYYYMMDD' ) , TO_TIMESTAMP ( '13-01-2020' , 'DD-MM-YYYY' ) ) ) < 0 THEN 'No Goods Receipt, but still in due date tolerance buffer' WHEN DAYS_BETWEEN ( TO_TIMESTAMP ( PU_LAST ( "EKPO" , "EKES"."EINDT" , "EKES"."EBTYP" = 'AB' ) , 'YYYYMMDD' ) , TO_TIMESTAMP ( PU_LAST ( "EKPO" , "EKBE"."CPUDT" , "EKBE"."VGABE" = '1' AND "EKBE"."SHKZG" = 'S' ) , 'YYYYMMDD' ) ) <= 1 AND DAYS_BETWEEN ( TO_TIMESTAMP ( PU_LAST ( "EKPO" , "EKES"."EINDT" , "EKES"."EBTYP" = 'AB' ) , 'YYYYMMDD' ) , TO_TIMESTAMP ( PU_LAST ( "EKPO" , "EKBE"."CPUDT" , "EKBE"."VGABE" = '1' AND "EKBE"."SHKZG" = 'S' ) , 'YYYYMMDD' ) ) >= ( -1.0 * 1 ) THEN 'Delivery on time' WHEN DAYS_BETWEEN ( TO_TIMESTAMP ( PU_LAST ( "EKPO" , "EKES"."EINDT" , "EKES"."EBTYP" = 'AB' ) , 'YYYYMMDD' ) , TO_TIMESTAMP ( PU_LAST ( "EKPO" , "EKBE"."CPUDT" , "EKBE"."VGABE" = '1' AND "EKBE"."SHKZG" = 'S' ) , 'YYYYMMDD' ) ) > 1 THEN 'Delivery too late' WHEN DAYS_BETWEEN ( TO_TIMESTAMP ( PU_LAST ( "EKPO" , "EKES"."EINDT" , "EKES"."EBTYP" = 'AB' ) , 'YYYYMMDD' ) , TO_TIMESTAMP ( PU_LAST ( "EKPO" , "EKBE"."CPUDT" , "EKBE"."VGABE" = '1' AND "EKBE"."SHKZG" = 'S' ) , 'YYYYMMDD' ) ) < ( -1.0 * 1 ) THEN 'Delivery too early' WHEN ISNULL ( PU_LAST ( "EKPO" , "EKES"."EINDT" , "EKES"."EBTYP" = 'AB' ) ) = 1 AND ISNULL ( PU_LAST ( "EKPO" , "EKBE"."CPUDT" , "EKBE"."VGABE" = '1' AND "EKBE"."SHKZG" = 'S' ) ) = 1 THEN 'No Goods Receipt and No On-Time Delivery Date' WHEN ISNULL ( PU_LAST ( "EKPO" , "EKES"."EINDT" , "EKES"."EBTYP" = 'AB' ) ) = 1 THEN 'Goods Receipt but No On-Time Delivery Date' ELSE 'Other' END ) AS "#{classification}"

axis2.name: #{TooEarly}
axis2.text:
AVG(CASE WHEN (CASE
   WHEN ISNULL(<%= GR_VARIABLE %>) = 1 AND (DATEDIFF(dd,TO_TIMESTAMP ( <%= Due_Date %>, 'YYYYMMDD' ), TO_TIMESTAMP(<%=Days_back%>, 'DD-MM-YYYY')))  >= 0 THEN 'No Goods Receipt and Future Due Date'
   WHEN ISNULL(<%= GR_VARIABLE %>) = 1 AND (DATEDIFF(dd,TO_TIMESTAMP ( <%= Due_Date %>, 'YYYYMMDD' ), TO_TIMESTAMP(<%=Days_back%>, 'DD-MM-YYYY')))  < (-1.0 * <%= OTD_upper %>) THEN 'No Goods Receipt and Due Date passed (Overdue)'
   WHEN ISNULL(<%= GR_VARIABLE %>) = 1 AND (DATEDIFF(dd,TO_TIMESTAMP ( <%= Due_Date %>, 'YYYYMMDD' ), TO_TIMESTAMP(<%=Days_back%>, 'DD-MM-YYYY'))) < 0 THEN 'No Goods Receipt, but still in due date tolerance buffer' 
   WHEN DAYS_BETWEEN(TO_TIMESTAMP ( <%= Due_Date %>, 'YYYYMMDD' ), TO_TIMESTAMP ( <%= GR_VARIABLE %>, 'YYYYMMDD' )) <= <%= OTD_upper %> 
    AND DAYS_BETWEEN(TO_TIMESTAMP ( <%= Due_Date %>, 'YYYYMMDD' ), TO_TIMESTAMP ( <%= GR_VARIABLE %>, 'YYYYMMDD' )) >= (-1.0 * <%= OTD_lower %>) 
        THEN 'Delivery on time'
   WHEN DAYS_BETWEEN(TO_TIMESTAMP ( <%= Due_Date %>, 'YYYYMMDD' ), TO_TIMESTAMP ( <%= GR_VARIABLE %>, 'YYYYMMDD' )) > <%= OTD_upper %> THEN 'Delivery too late'
   WHEN DAYS_BETWEEN(TO_TIMESTAMP ( <%= Due_Date %>, 'YYYYMMDD' ), TO_TIMESTAMP ( <%= GR_VARIABLE %>, 'YYYYMMDD' )) < (-1.0 * <%= OTD_lower %>) THEN 'Delivery too early'
   WHEN ISNULL(<%= Due_Date%>) = 1 AND ISNULL(<%= GR_VARIABLE %>) = 1 THEN 'No Goods Receipt and No On-Time Delivery Date'
   WHEN ISNULL(<%= Due_Date%>) = 1 THEN 'Goods Receipt but No On-Time Delivery Date'
   ELSE 'Other'
END) = 'Delivery too early'
THEN 1.0 ELSE 0.0 END)
